      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-02-28T20:03:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You need a mode argument here, because this creates a file (even though you don’t need to say O_CREAT). Here, 0600 or the symbolic form S_IRUSR | S_IWUSR are the only choices that makes any sense.",
      "revId": "cb2e1ef13f5704284b49e3b90b84ac5e4eb4f56f",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
